  <official_title>An Open-label, Randomized, Multicenter, Active-controlled, Dose-ranging Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Albinterferon Alfa 2b Administered Every 4 Weeks Plus Ribavirin in Interferon Alfa-naïve Patients With Genotype 2/3 Chronic Hepatitis C</official_title>
